Package org.rapidcontext.util

Interface HttpUtil.HEADER

Enclosing interface:
HttpUtil
public static interface HttpUtil.HEADER
A number of standard HTTP headers as defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0) and RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1).
